{
  "stem": "1511.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, I went-- I was in my friend's place, Malcha-- Balcha--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Balcha-- Balcha, her name was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's so many years, hard to remember the names and everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she figure out she want to save my life and how to save my life.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So she put me under a cupboard in her kitchen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had little cupboards there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a small house with a little kitchen, and I was sitting.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And her sister got married to one of the officers from the Russian army.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's why I was safe in there, because they would never come.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When a Russian lives with a wife in the same place--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was Jewish army guys.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- but I was only coming out once in a while at night.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in the daytime, if somebody comes and knocks at the door, I wasn't visible.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wasn't there, but I was sitting over there with my feet like that, and just like that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was going on for weeks, and when she came home, she brought something to eat.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She went to a dressmaker to sew, made a few cents, and she helped me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, the whole family there, all the girls were living together with that guy, with his wife, too.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But after a few weeks, or maybe two months, or more than that, I can't remember the time-- I couldn't get out of the-- under the cupboard, because I couldn't stretch my feet out and I was in terrible pain.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I did get up, I had-- my blood turned into gangrene, and I had big lumps on here, and here, and wherever you want, and under here, and here-- and every place, and here, big lumps.",
      "word_count": 38
    }
  ],
